quran[6{c,v,t}:
35,39,"wohi to hai jis ne tum ko zameen mein khalifa banaya hai ab jo koi kufar karta hai is ke kufar ka wabaal usi par hai, aur kafiroon ko unn ka kufar iss ke siwa koi taraqqi nahi deta ke un ke rab ka ghazab unn par ziyada se ziyada bharakta chala jata hai kafiroon ke liye khasaray mein izafay ke siwa koi taraqqi nahi"
35,40,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) un se kaho,"" kabhi tum ne dekha bhi hai apne unn sharikon ko jinhein tum khuda ko chore kar puraka karte ho? mujhe batao, unhon ne zameen mein kya peda kya hai? ya asmano mein un ki kya shirkat hai""? ( agar yeh nahi bta satke to un se pucho ) kya hum ne inhen koi tehreer likh kar di hai jis ki bana par yeh ( apne is shirk ke liye ) koi saaf sanad rakhtay hon? nahi, balkay yeh zalim aik dosray ko mehez fraib ke jhansey diye ja rahay hain"
35,41,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah hi hai jo asmano aur zameen ko tal jaane se rokay hue hai, aur agar woh tal jayen to Allah ke baad koi dosra inhen thaamnay wala nahi hai be shak Allah bara Haleem aur dar guzar frmane wala hai"
35,42,yeh log kari kari kasmain kha kar kaha karte thay ke agar koi khabardaar karne wala un ke haan aa gaya hota to yeh duniya ki har doosri qoum se barh kar raast ro hotay magar jab khabardaar karne wala un ke paas agaya to is ki aamad ne inn ke andar haq se faraar ke siwa kisi cheez mein izafah nah kya
35,43,"yeh zameen mein aur ziyada اistakbar karne lagey aur buri buri chaalein chalne lagey, halaank burii chaalein apne chalne walon hi ko le bithti hain ab kya yeh log iss ka intzaar kar rahay hain ke pichli qomon ke sath Allah ka jo tareeqa raha hai wohi inn ke sath bhi brta jaye? yahi baat hai to tum Allah ke tareeqay mein hargiz koi tabdeeli nah pao ge aur tum kabhi nah dekho ge ke Allah ki sunnat ko is ke muqarrar rastay se koi taaqat phair sakti hai"
35,44,"kya yeh log zameen mein kabhi chalay phiray nahi hain ke inhen unn logon ka injaam nazar aata jo inn se pehlay guzar chuke hain aur un se bohat ziyada taaqat war thay? Allah ko koi cheez aajiz karne wali nahi hai, nah asmano mein aur nah zameen mein woh sab kuch jaanta hai aur har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
